{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EdTech Platform</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #d32f2f; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #b71c1c 3px solid; /* Darker red for contrast */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        #showcase {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/d32f2f/ffffff?text=Inspiring+Learning') no-repeat center center/cover; /* Red background with placeholder image */\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #showcase::before {\n            content: \"\";\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.7); /* Semi-transparent red overlay */\n        }\n        #showcase h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #showcase p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h3 {\n            color: #d32f2f; /* Red brand color */\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .feature {\n            width: 30%;\n            float: left;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 1.5%;\n            background: #fff;\n            border-left: 5px solid #d32f2f; /* Red border */\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .feature h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #d32f2f; /* Red brand color */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background: #333;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background: #d32f2f; /* Red brand color */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .button:hover {\n            background: #b71c1c; /* Darker red on hover */\n        }\n        .clearfix::after {\n            content: \"\";\n            clear: both;\n            display: table;\n        }\n\n        @media(max-width: 768px){\n            .feature{\n                width: 100%;\n                float: none;\n                margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n            #showcase h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>EduSpark</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"showcase\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ignite Your Learning Journey</h2>\n            <p>Unlock your potential with our innovative and engaging online courses. Learn at your own pace, from anywhere.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">Get Started Today</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <main class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"main-content\">\n            <h3>Why Choose EduSpark?</h3>\n            <div class=\"feature clearfix\">\n                <h4>Expert Instructors</h4>\n                <p>Learn from industry leaders and passionate educators who bring real-world experience to the classroom.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature clearfix\">\n                <h4>Interactive Learning</h4>\n                <p>Engage with dynamic content, quizzes, and projects designed for maximum retention and understanding.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature clearfix\">\n                <h4>Flexible Paths</h4>\n                <p>Choose from a wide range of courses tailored to your interests and career goals, with flexible learning schedules.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EduSpark. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}